Have fun with my conf files ;)

Software I use on my Arch laptop (CLI oriented :D):

SLIM : Login Manager
EarthQuake (gem) : Twitter client
Xscreensaver
Awesome : Windows Manager
urxvt : terminal
Vim : text editor
Ranger : file browser
Weechat : irc client (irssi is great too)
Pry (gem) : ruby interpreter
iPython : python interpreter
xrandr : multiscreen

